Please see the online documentation at:
http://www.barricklab.org/twiki/bin/view/Lab/ToolsBacterialGenomeResequencing


==== Installation Instructions ====

== Perl Modules ==

> sudo perl -MCPAN -e shell
> install Math::Pari
> install Statistics::Distributions
> force install CJFIELDS/BioPerl-1.6.1.tar.gz

== Mac OS 10.6 (Snow Leopard) ==

sudo port install boost
sudo port install boost-build
sudo port install pari

create the file "user-config.jam" in your home directory
